{"tid":1285450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文。整合]香港人，我知道你攰，但唔好放棄！","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:48:19.000Z","uid":115041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c292a571104f8c3d71a09bcf3ebdf6aa738d1ea","tid":1285450,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"經過一個6月，我相信大家都好攰，我留意到連登都開始失焦，留意返，我地爭取既5大訴求，一樣都未爭取到！而且，我唔係轉移注意力，但如果你睇得清香港未來，一定要有真民主，同埋好似佛地魔咁唔提得既港獨，冷靜，睇埋落去先。<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家先休息，但記住我地要隨時再行動，除左野餐，我地仲有好多功夫可以做，去達成短期既5大訴求，以及長遠目標。<br />\n<br />\n短期上<br />\n1.要有野餐既準備，如果有民陣，或者網友自發既野餐，一定要keep到一定人數，話俾政府知，仲有咁多人抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n76遊行<br />\n7/6光復屯門公園大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280848</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n77遊行<br />\n[文宣] 7.7九龍區大遊行 宣傳圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285345</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2.野餐前要準備好自己，自保身分同埋人身安全，不幸被捕都知要點做同幫助自己冷靜<br />\n<br />\n野餐裝備<br />\n[推到完場LIVE] 野餐後須知網上講座 [情緒支援及法律支援]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n[長期置頂必讀] 野餐裝備整合 (隱藏身份+防具篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n3.救義士<br />\n應對返keep人數同埋長期抗爭準備，義士一定要救，長期留意新聞，如果有能力，就法律援助佢地。或者去迫黑警公開原因細節<br />\n<br />\n緊急！天水圍天耀有個女仔比藍絲屈打人，急要片幫手！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n港台即時：已拉十三人衝立會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282466</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n4.國際力量，唔理有冇用，總知要俾世界長期關注香港，小層面上就靠自己外國朋友，中層面就搵外國媒體，大層面就睇下可以點迫外國直接介入<br />\n<br />\n國際力量<br />\n外相侯俊偉今天再一次警告中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n5.第四權，任何活動最好都放風俾記者，等佢地在場，記錄事實，愈多鏡頭愈好，當然，直接課金支持蘋果同立場都好重要，等佢地繼續運作。<br />\n<br />\n中長期上<br />\n1.多方面文宣，俾多啲香港人知道我地理念，目標係令更多中立變黃，令藍變中立，令和理非慢慢有勇氣勇武。<br />\n<br />\n港人港地youtube賣廣告，點破解<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282716</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2.做運動！增加自身野餐行動力，減少戰力損失同埋增加戰鬥力！<br />\n<br />\n全民健身計劃<br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地進行義教，識，唔識都可以歡迎咁多位巴絲加入<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 呢個谷唔講任何政治 <br />\n只係單純想出嚟約大家做下健身 <br />\n記住 我地健身目的係為左以後俾人追可以跑快啲，搬野可以搬重啲,有危險可以保護到自己！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=ee99f2a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，知大家都攰，我整左兩個播放清單，目的俾俾大家沉澱一下6月，有動力繼續，以及用證據去證明中共幾仆街。<br />\n<br />\n同時，有個ig會不定時放關於香港歷史既知識，片段，俾大家了解香港係點變成咁，同埋反思一下以往，從歷史中學習。<br />\n<br />\nig: thestoryofhongkong<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我可以做既係咁多，兄弟爬山，各自努力，團結不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef2b0801dd429bccec95e2ce8c6bb2659708714","tid":1285450,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3816ea4d047796abf717c51d9d9794a6b6712a0","tid":1285450,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"無野講"},{"pid":"8451d78a7e94e3a558bb2adace69b35497a7393d","tid":1285450,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"playlist<br />\n<br />\n反共<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhD8SkeuqmFk3EYi7amOnSZYrKXOh8e8V\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLhD8SkeuqmFk3EYi7amOnSZYrKXOh8e8V&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=eec0d946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhD8SkeuqmFk3EYi7amOnSZYrKXOh8e8V</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhD8SkeuqmFn6cCVU0TrPAb9mM9mtx9fU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLhD8SkeuqmFn6cCVU0TrPAb9mM9mtx9fU&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=4c16c7a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhD8SkeuqmFn6cCVU0TrPAb9mM9mtx9fU</a>"},{"pid":"bdfb7e47d37cb80f0a69328fb2ae450f6e900f81","tid":1285450,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"eadedef4e6dd185ec8927ad731d45e834b96a9f9","tid":1285450,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好放棄"},{"pid":"35d3acd7000d4ffc75eb37313c793a37a0f0827c","tid":1285450,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:15:54.000Z","msg":"我只係想有用既抗爭post上多啲熱門"},{"pid":"a79638242f5599cfdd5a1f34f2c9caddc8917593","tid":1285450,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75abe68ccfa66b8ff01673c839530b74d1b57e93","tid":1285450,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79638242f5599cfdd5a1f34f2c9caddc8917593","tid":1285450,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，大家有同一個理念就得，休息好，再出黎保護前線"},{"pid":"abfda86642e3b98523c3eb88b3e32a350c31d8a1","tid":1285450,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"推多推"}]}